  <h3 class="pg-h">Comprehensive Consultation</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">We begin with a thorough evaluation of your hair loss pattern and medical history. Our specialists assess your scalp condition, discuss your concerns, and determine if PRP hair therapy is the right approach for your specific situation. This personalized assessment ensures we create the most effective treatment plan.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/8f8c6668ef95.jpeg" alt="Woman Getting Hair Restoration PRP" width="121" height="121" loading="lazy" />
  <h3 class="pg-h">Customized Treatment Session</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">The procedure begins with a simple blood draw, similar to a routine lab test. Your blood is then processed in a centrifuge to separate and concentrate the platelet-rich plasma. After applying a topical anesthetic for comfort, the PRP is precisely injected into targeted areas of your scalp to stimulate dormant hair follicles.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/6b91c35eb686.jpeg" alt="Before &amp; After Woman Hair Restoration" width="121" height="121" loading="lazy" />
